<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<%- include ./partials/head -%>
	</head>
	<body>
		<h1>LTI Launch Instructions</h1>
		<h2>Configuration XML</h2>

		<p>View the LTI <a href="<%= xml_url %>">configuration xml</a></p>
		<p>This configuration is used to install your LTI tool into an LSM.  This xml can be referenced by url or copied and pasted durring the install process.</p>

		<h2>LTI Launch</h2>
		<p>View the LTI <a href="<%= launch_url %>">launch endpoint</a></p>
		<p>Note, this url is typically sent a POST request with all sorts of LTI data.  If you access it directly, it'll display an error page indicating your request did not validate.</p>

		<h3>Testing LTI Launch</h3>
		<ol>
			<li>Visit the <a href="http://lti.tools/saltire/tc">IMS LTI Tool Consumer Emulator</a></li>
			<li>Set <b>Launch URL</b> to <span><%= launch_url %></span></li>
			<li>Set <b>Consmer key</b> to the value defined in <span>config/settings.json</span></li>
			<li>Set <b>Shared secret</b> to the value defined in <span>config/settings.json</span></li>
		</ol>
	</body>
</html>
